song_lyrics: Sundar Shyām chhabi avilokī, lājat koṭik kām...
Shvet basan tan shvet ābhukhan, shvet pushpa ur dām;
Bolat vachan sunat sukh upjat, ānand āṭho jām... mano 1
Sundar pāg bhāg par ujval, nain kamal gun dhām;
Premānand dhārī chhabi antar, raṭat nīrantar nām... mano 2
title: Manohar shobhit Shrī Ghanshyām
